<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Bantaeng Digital Map</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0f1115;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #00d2d3;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 210, 211, 0.4);
        }

        header p {
            color: #84817a;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Container Peta / Daftar Lokasi */
        .map-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1100px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Kartu Lokasi (Konsep Peta Buta) */
        .location-card {
            position: relative;
            background: #1e272e;
            width: 300px;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px dashed #485460;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Efek saat kursor hover atau kartu aktif (disentuh) */
        .location-card:hover, .location-card.active {
            border-style: solid;
            border-color: #00d2d3;
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 210, 211, 0.25);
        }

        /* Tampilan Default Nama Tempat */
        .blind-map-label {
            text-align: center;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .blind-map-label .radar-icon {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .blind-map-label h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #dcdde1;
        }

        /* Konten Tersembunyi (Foto & Info) */
        .hidden-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.95);
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Foto Tempat */
        .hidden-content img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: brightness(0.65);
            transition: transform 0.8s ease;
        }

        /* Zoom in sedikit fotonya saat di-hover */
        .location-card:hover .hidden-content img,
        .location-card.active .hidden-content img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Detail Info teks */
        .info-panel {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95) 35%);
            padding: 25px 20px;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .info-panel h3 {
            color: #00d2d3;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .info-panel p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #f5f6fa;
        }

        /* LOGIKA PEMBACAAN HOVER / ACTIVE */
        .location-card:hover .blind-map-label,
        .location-card.active .blind-map-label {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.8);
        }

        .location-card:hover .hidden-content,
        .location-card.active .hidden-content {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
            z-index: 3;
        }

        .location-card:hover .info-panel,
        .location-card.active .info-panel {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Animasi Berdenyut untuk Icon */
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }
        }

        /* Responsif untuk layar HP */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .map-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>The Bantaeng Digital Map</h1>
        <p>Sentuh atau dekatkan kursor pada nama lokasi untuk membuka keindahannya</p>
    </header>

    <div class="map-container">

        <div class="location-card">
            <div class="blind-map-label">
                <span class="radar-icon">🌊</span>
                <h2>SERUNI</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden-content">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Pantai Seruni">
                <div class="info-panel">
                    <h3>Pantai Seruni</h3>
                    <p>Kawasan ikonik berupa ruang publik estetik di pesisir Bantaeng. Menjadi pusat kuliner, olahraga, dan tempat terbaik warga menikmati senja.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="location-card">
            <div class="blind-map-label">
                <span class="radar-icon">🌿</span>
                <h2>EREMERASA</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden-content">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546182990-dffeafbe841d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Permandian Eremerasa">
                <div class="info-panel">
                    <h3>Eremerasa</h3>
                    <p>Pemandian alam legendaris dengan air yang sangat jernih dan sejuk. Airnya mengalir langsung dari mata air alami di bawah naungan pohon-pohon rindang purba.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="location-card">
            <div class="blind-map-label">
                <span class="radar-icon">🏔️</span>
                <h2>LOKA</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden-content">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Agrowisata Loka">
                <div class="info-panel">
                    <h3>Agrowisata Loka</h3>
                    <p>Terletak di kawasan dataran tinggi pegunungan Bantaeng. Menyuguhkan udara dingin yang segar, panorama hijau memukau, serta perkebunan stroberi dan sayuran lokal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <script>
        // JavaScript digunakan khusus untuk menangani interaksi layar sentuh (HP/Tablet)
        // Karena event :hover di CSS terkadang tidak berjalan sempurna di perangkat mobile.
        const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.location-card');

        cards.forEach(card => {
            // Ketika jari menyentuh elemen
            card.addEventListener('touchstart', function(e) {
                // Menghilangkan efek aktif dari kartu lain jika ada
                cards.forEach(c => {
                    if (c !== card) c.classList.remove('active');
                });
                
                // Mengaktifkan/menonaktifkan kartu yang sedang disentuh
                this.classList.toggle('active');
            });
        });

        // Menutup informasi jika pengguna menyentuh area kosong di luar kartu
        document.body.addEventListener('touchstart', function(e) {
            if (!e.target.closest('.location-card')) {
                cards.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
